howtoplay.trading.title: How to Play : Trading With Enderlings
howtoplay.trading.text.1: You can trade with a new mob named the Enderling, which spawns randomly in any of the End Biomes inside of the End Dimension. They offer goods such as ender pearls, cooked skipper, crystal apples, and tons of other useful items!
howtoplay.trading.text.2: The Enderling will trade in exchange for Ender Ingots, which can be obtained from the new Ender Ores. This new ore only spawns in the End Dimension, and can be found on the bottoms of the massive end islands.
howtoplay.trading.text.3: Once you break an Ender Ore, it will drop Raw Ender, which you can take to a furnace or a blast furnace to have smelted into the new Ender Ingot!
howtoplay.trading.text.4: This new ingot can be hard to obtain, so the trading rewards can be well worth your time!
